<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="no" ?>
<modDesc descVersion="107">
    <author>Ozz</author>
    <version>1.0.0.0</version>
    <iconFilename>icon_UsedEquipmentYards.dds</iconFilename>
    <title>
        <en>Used Equipment Yards</en>
        <de>Gebrauchtgerätelager</de>
        <fr>Cours de matériel d'occasion</fr>
    </title>
    <description>
        <en><![CDATA[Allows you to define custom vehicle sale yards that you can visit and buy used equipment from. Draw yard boundaries in-game, configure inventory, and watch equipment spawn and despawn dynamically.

        Beta Changelog:

        - Tightened up the pricing variance and also scaled it by price. 
        - Yards track recent sales so you can no longer sell back equipment to a yard for profit.
        - Returning a running vehicle will stop the motor.


GitHub: https://github.com/sprkem/FS25_UsedEquipmentYards]]>
        </en>
        <de><![CDATA[Ermöglicht das Definieren benutzerdefinierter Fahrzeugverkaufsplätze, auf denen Sie gebrauchte Ausrüstung kaufen können.]]></de>
        <fr><![CDATA[Permet de définir des cours de vente de véhicules personnalisées où vous pouvez acheter de l'équipement d'occasion.]]></fr>
    </description>
